These MODs ("Works") are created by Xen-Shuto ("Author") using the Stellaris
Portrait Mod Template. This license applies to all portrait mods contained 
within this repository. By downloading or using the Works, you agree to the 
following terms.

1. COPYRIGHT
Copyright (c) 2025 Xen-Shuto. All rights to the Works belong to the Author.

2. PERMISSIONS
You may download and use the Works in your Stellaris game. You may study the
Works as a reference and create your own original mods inspired by them. Use
of your own original mods for non-commercial purposes is permitted.

3. RESTRICTIONS
The following actions are strictly prohibited:
- Redistributing or publishing any of these Works as your own work.
- Modifying these Works and publishing the modified versions.
- Using or distributing these Works as if they were templates.
- Impersonating the Author or presenting these Works as official content 
  from Paradox Interactive or any other third party.
If you wish to create a modified mod, please use the original Template
instead of modifying these Works directly: 

Species Portrait Template
https://github.com/Xen-Shuto/species_portrait_template

4. COMMERCIAL USE
Commercial use of the Works or any derivative works is prohibited.

5. DISCLAIMER AND LIABILITY
THE WORKS ARE PROVIDED "AS IS", WITHOUT WARRANTY OF ANY KIND. THE AUTHOR
SHALL NOT BE LIABLE FOR ANY DAMAGES ARISING FROM THE USE OF THE WORKS.
These Works are unofficial fan content and are not endorsed by or affiliated
with Paradox Interactive.

6. GOVERNING LAW
This license is governed by the laws of Japan.

